elti, Celestino Deleyto, David Desser, Thomas Elsaesser, Steve Neale, Thomas Schatz, Paul Schrader, Vivian Sobchack, Janet Staiger, Linda Williams, and Robin Wood.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Nov 2021) 0aMotion picture playsxHistory and criticism. 7aPERFORMING ARTS / General.2bisacsh1 aAltman, Rick, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aBourget, Jean-Loup, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aBuscombe, Edward, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aCawelti, John G., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aCordova, Richard De, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aDeleyto, Celestino, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aDesser, David, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aElsaesser, Thomas, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aFeuer, Jane, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aGallagher, Tag, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aGrant, Barry Keith, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aGrant, Barry Keith, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aHess Wright, Judith, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aHigson, Andrew, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aJeffords, Susan, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aKawin, Bruce F., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aKlinger, Barbara, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aMitchell, Edward, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aNeale, Steve, econtributor